        {
            "title": "樂普生物折讓10.99%配股籌4.71億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">樂普生物(02157)公布，擬配售9382.5萬股集資約4.71億元，配股價5.02元，較該股昨收市價5.64元折讓約10.99%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"樂普生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/lepu_1200.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"樂普生物官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/lepu_1200.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">樂普生物官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若與該股前5個交易日平均收市價5.58元計，配股價較之折讓10.1%；以前30個交易日平均收市價5.24元比較，配股價則折讓約4.19%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">預期配股集資淨額約4.63億元，樂普生物擬將其中約20%用於投資核心產品MRG003 (EGFR-ADC)的商業化及市場推廣；約60%用於核心產品的臨床試驗推進；約20%用於新產品管線的研發。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15062647-%e6%a8%82%e6%99%ae%e7%94%9f%e7%89%a9%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9310-99%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c4-71%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240517_FI_source-web_02157.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-04 08:55:28",
