        {
            "title": "黑期失守二萬四低水逾140點 阿里發換股債其ADR仍高水0.4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時13分跌83點或0.35%，報23923點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報24043點，較香港上日現貨收市低26點或0.11%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣498.8元，較上日香港收市低2.17元或0.43%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣106.6元，較上日香港收市高0.42元或0.4%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣122.3元，較上日香港收市低0.5元或0.41%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣125.8元，較上日香港收市高0.53元或0.42%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣57.8元，較上日香港收市低0.25元或0.43%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230829-130650_20230810_FI_source-web_09988-7_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230829-130650_20230810_FI_source-web_09988-7_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣95.2元，較上日香港收市高0.36元或0.38%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣72.5元，較上日香港收市高0.16元或0.22%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣416.2元，較上日香港收市低1元或0.24%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣50.1元，較上日香港收市高0.04元或0.08%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣8.1元，較上日香港收市低0.02元或0.29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報23991點，跌61點，較上日恒指收市24069點，低水79點。科指期貨夜市收報5205點，較上日科指收市低水29點；國指期貨夜市收報8609點，較上日國指收市低水39點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15062590-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%88%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e5%9b%9b%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be140%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e7%99%bc%e6%8f%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%82%b5%e5%85%b6adr%e4%bb%8d%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b40-4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-04 08:20:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "融創中國上月合同銷售按年3.84倍 上半年仍跌10.39%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">融創中國(01918)公布，今年6月份合同銷售按年急增3.84倍，但上半年累計仍較去年同期減少10.39%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：融創中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20230905_FI_source-web_01918_SUNAC_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：融創中國官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20230905_FI_source-web_01918_SUNAC_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：融創中國官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司今年6月份合同銷售約75.5億元(人民幣．下同)，較去年同期的15.6億元大幅提升；涉及樓面12.9萬平方米，均價約每平方米5.85萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將上半年6個月累積計算，累計實現合同銷售約235.5億元，按年減少10.39%；涉及樓面約72.1萬平方米，均價約每平方米3.27萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15062575-%e8%9e%8d%e5%89%b5%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b43-84%e5%80%8d-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e4%bb%8d%e8%b7%8c10-39",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/01918-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-04 08:15:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "羅兵咸永道晉升23名新合夥人",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">羅兵咸永道公布，今年在區內晉升23名新合夥人，任命從7月1日起生效，覆蓋審計、稅務和諮詢業務，女性佔比接近半數（48%），彰顯該行對多元化及包容性工作環境的承諾。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據了解，羅兵咸永道今年新合夥人人數與往年相若。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">羅兵咸永道表示，今年較早前完成業務架構重組，形成四大核心業務——審計及鑒證服務、稅務服務、交易服務和管理諮詢。公司將通過聚焦三大戰略領域：深化重點客戶合作、提供高品質的服務、吸引和留住頂尖人才，打造成為中國領先的專業服務機構。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">羅兵咸永道中國主席兼首席執行官何睦寧（Hemione Hudson）形容「已做好充分準備帶領羅兵咸永道中國開啟新的篇章」。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15061523-%e7%be%85%e5%85%b5%e5%92%b8%e6%b0%b8%e9%81%93%e6%99%89%e5%8d%8723%e5%90%8d%e6%96%b0%e5%90%88%e5%a4%a5%e4%ba%ba",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240913_CR_source-web_pwc-e1726230859100.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-03 17:20:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
